LOW TAXES!! Bright and cheery living room has a brand new Anderson bay window and new recessed lighting. Gorgeous kitchen has been totally renovated with granite countertops, new white wood cabinets, recessed lighting, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and an OVER-SIZED island with two stools. Beautiful wood flooring has been installed throughout the main level of the home. Upstairs you will find the master bedroom complete with updated bathroom with new vanity, tile shower with glass door and tile flooring.  Two other good-sized bedrooms and another fully renovated bathroom complete the level. Three new ceiling fans with light packages have also been installed. Lower level family room has newer flooring, ceiling fan light combo and access to the 2 car garage, laundry room and powder room. The back deck is a great place to entertain or just to watch the little ones play. Loads of TECHNOLOGY upgrades include: smart stove with air fryer, smart thermostats, smart google light switches, electric car charging cable installed in garage, most of the home has been wired with CAT6 network cable. Other amenities include: NEWER roof, NEWER central air, NEW sewer line, upgraded 200 amp service, over-sized 2 car garage, NEW quiet garage door opener, NEW doorbell chime, NEW oil tank and most of the home has been freshly painted. Only minutes to Merck, turnpike, Septa R5 regional rail and all major roadways. TAKE ADVANTAGE OF FALLING INTEREST RATES.  Make your appointment today.  Be sure to check out the 3D Virtual Tour.
